Semantic Machine Reading (beyond text)

Specify language for slot-filling problem description.


Language Requirements: 

Problem Description using Templates:

	Entity-Type: Slot(*), Entity-SubType(*), Entity-SuperType(*)

	Slot: Cardinality(1), Annotation(*), Evaluation-Function (1) 

	Annotation: Entity-Type(1), Char-Offset(?), Surfaceform(?)
	
	Evaluation-Function: 
			Entity-Type Evaluation
			Value Evaluation: Normalization-Function
	
	Normalization-Function:
			Identity (default)  
			Normalization
	
	Cardinality: 
		SingleValue
		MultiValue
			List: Min (int +) , Max (int + && > min)
			Set: Min (int +) , Max (int + && > min)
Domain-Description:

	Entity-Type: Entity-SubType, Entity-SuperType
	Entity-SubType: Entity-SubType, Entity-SuperType
	Entity-SuperType: Entity-SubType, Entity-SuperType

	Domain-constraints: Constraint

Document-Description:

	Document-specific constraints: Constraint

		Hard-Constraint_Exclude_Slot_Type (Includes other):
			Exclude: (Slot, Type)
			
		Hard-Constraint_Include_Slot_Type (Excludes other):
			Include: (Slot, Type)

		Hard-Constraint_Exclude_Slot_Type_Pair (Includes other):
			With: (Slot, Type)
			Exclude: (Slot, Type)
			
		Hard-Constraint_Include_Slot_Type_Pair (Excludes other):
			With: (Slot, Type)
			Include: (Slot, Type)

		Hard-Constraint_Include_Type (Excludes other):
			Include: Type

		Hard-Constraint_Excludes_Type (Includes other):
			Exclude: Type

		Hard-Constaint_Include_Value_Range (Excludes other):
			Include: Type, From, To

		Hard-Constaint_Excludes_Value_Range (Includes other):
			Excludes: Type, From, To

		Hard-Constaint_Include_Value_Range_Slot_Pair (Excludes other):
			With: (Slot, Type)			
			Include: Slot(optional), Type, From, To

		Hard-Constaint_Excludes_Value_Range_Slot_Pair (Includes other):
			With: (Slot, Type)			
			Excludes: Slot(optional), Type, From, To


Entity-Type Lexicalization:

Lexical Entry:
	Entity-Type, Text

Regular-Expression Entry:
	Enitty-Type, Regular-Expression
	
 

